  const addProduct = (item) => {
    switch (item.type) {
      case "doorBell":    setDoorBells([...doorBells, item]);
      
    }

  return (
    <DataContext.Provider
      value={{ doorBells,addProduct, doorLocks, lightings, speakers, thermostats }}

      {children}

export const useData = () => {
  return useContext(DataContext);
};
